            , were indicted for <rs id="t17930529-83-off455" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17930529-83-off455" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17930529-83-off455" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t17930529-83-cd456" type="crimeDate">28th of May</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17930529-83-off455 t17930529-83-cd456"></join>, a pair of leather boots, value 10 d. a muslin neckcloth, value 3 d. and seven shillings in money
            </rs>; the goods, chattels and monies of 
               
                  <persName id="t17930529-83-victim983" type="victimName">
                     James 
                     Farrell
                  <interp inst="t17930529-83-victim983" type="surname" value="Farrell"></interp>
